summary: An Ordinance appropriating Thirty-three Thousand Three Hundred Thirty-five Dollars ($33,335.00) of the funds in the Cedar River Water Shed Condemnation Fund to pay the State of Washington certain awards and court costs for the taking of certain state lands in Cause No. 75069 of the Superior Court of the State of Washington for King County, under Ordinance No. 22305 of the City of Seattle.
